<D>__{ten four. get out of there.}
<C>__{charlie}
<D>__{we're gone. over and out.}
<A>__{charlie hangs up the radio. he starts writing on a clipboard. silence for a few moments, and then charlie notices tom staring at him.}
<C>__{charlie}
<D>__{what?}
