<D>__{yeah, building a home, raising a family that's just stupid.}
<C>__{tom}
<D>__{i didn't say that!}
<C>__{charlie}
<D>__{you know what, tom? i really don't give a shit what you said.}
<A>__{tom doesn't reply. charlie puts the truck in gear; starts off. tom looks at charlie, shakes his head what was that about?}
